99
00:09:52,460 --> 00:09:55,420
At that time, Vietnam was devastated by the war.

100
00:09:55,820 --> 00:10:03,820
Our civil infrastructure and industry had been bombed into non-existence, and we could not trade with most other nations.

101
00:10:04,540 --> 00:10:08,700
By the late 1980s, Vietnam was on the verge of nationwide famine.

102
00:10:09,260 --> 00:10:16,380
Millions of lives were at stake, and our only strong allies, the USSR, was no longer in a position to help.

103
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:19,340
For all these reasons, in 1986, Vietnam.

104
