108
00:10:59,948 --> 00:11:11,868
We had to pay millions of dollars to the United States to compensate them for the very money and weapons which were used to massacre Vietnamese civilians during the war.

109
00:11:12,508 --> 00:11:15,708
Vietnam had no choice but to accept the terms of the empire.

110
00:11:16,540 --> 00:11:21,340
